title: S3 EP2: Murder? ... Anyone? ... Anyone? ... Bueller? with Michael McMurray
description:
This week, Maggie and Tim are joined by cinematographer and director Michael McMurray to talk about Season 3 Episode 2: Murder? ... Anyone? ... Anyone? ... Bueller? The episode where Shawn thinks a murder has occurred at his high school reunion. The only problem is there's no evidence to prove a crime happened!
